init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf came to the 92nd little pig's house and said, "Little pig, little pig, let me come in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm not going to let you in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Please let me in," pleaded the wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Little pig, little pig, let me come in," said the wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf tried to open the door, but it was locked.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Little pig, let me come in," he wheezed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The pig continued to ignore him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Little pig, let me come in," he wailed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He cried and cried and cried.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They fell on the ground and made puddles.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: of tears landed on the handle of the door.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf cried and cried and cried.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf cried until he had no more tears left.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf was so surprised and confused that he forgot to be hungry.
